translated: Eriksson, Henry Emanuel, pastor, Uleberg, born July 13, 1907 in Brålanda, Älvsborg County, son of merchant Johannes E. and Sara Eriksson. Married in 1939 to Rut Peterson. Children: Karin Elisabeth, born 1945 and Jan Henry, born 1947. Completed secondary school in Gothenburg in 1929, theological degree in 1931, passed practical theology exam and pastoral examination for Karlstad Diocese in 1934. Served as temporary pastor and assistant pastor in Bolstad, assistant pastor in Gestad, and later as pastor in Bolstad and Gestad from 1939.
